 system without a frontend. The evaluation of the API system will be conducted and then the NLP model will be developed which includes the preprocessing, model architecture design, model training, and fine tuning of the system. The model will then be displayed after the front-end development and the backend development will help in setting up the backend with database integration. Finally, a final documentation of the whole project will be done accordingly as shown in the Gantt Chart below.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFigure 34 Proposed Gantt Chart\r\n\r\nUpdated Gantt Chart\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFigure 35 Final Gantt Chart\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nReferences\r\n\r\nAdhikari, S., M. & R., 2020. NLP based Machine Learning Approaches for Text Summarization. [Online] \r\nAvailable at: https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9076358\r\n[Accessed 10 August 2023].\r\n\r\nHaider, M. M., Hossin, M. A., Mahi, H. R. & Arif, H., 2020. Automatic Text Summarization Using Gensim Word2Vec and K-Means Clustering Algorithm. Dhaka, Bangladesh, IEEE.\r\n\r\nIBM, 2023. What is Django. [Online] \r\nAvailable at: https://www.ibm.com/topics/django\r\n[Accessed 11 August 2023].\r\n\r\nJohnson, D., 2021. What is Trello? Here\'s what you need to know about the online project management tool. [Online] \r\nAvailable at: https://www.businessinsider.com/guides/tech/what-is-trello?op=1\r\n[Accessed 02 August 2023].\r\n\r\nKamarozaman, M.I.Z.B.I., Hafizzul, A.N.B.Y.M. and Bin, B.A.M.M.M., 2023. Speed Reading Tool Powered by Artificial Intelligence for Students with ADHD, Dyslexia, or Short Attention Span. arXiv preprint arXiv:2307.14544.\r\n\r\nKarani, D., 2018. Introduction to Word Embedding and Word2Vec. [Online] \r\nAvailable at: https://towardsdatascience.com/introduction-to-word-embedding-and-word2vec-652d0c2060fa\r\n[Accessed 15 September 2023].\r\n\r\nLu, G., Larcher, S.B. and Tran, T., 2023. Hybrid Long Document Summarization using C2F-FAR and ChatGPT: A Practical Study. arX