	(49, 2, 'Sprint Backlog-1.docx', 19105, 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document', 'Sprint Backlog\r\n\r\nUser Management System (UM)\r\n\r\nS.N.\r\n\r\nKey\r\n\r\nEpic\r\n\r\nStory\r\n\r\n1.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nNew User Registration\r\n\r\nCreate user registration form with username, full name, email and password fields.\r\n\r\nImplement backend logic to store the user registration in the database.\r\n\r\nDisplay a success message upon successful registration.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLogin for Registered User\r\n\r\nCreate a login page with username and password fields.\r\n\r\nImplement authentication logic verify user credentials.\r\n\r\nRedirect the user to the home page upon successful login.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLogout the Logged in User\r\n\r\nAdd a logout button in the navigation bar with popup model.\r\n\r\nImplement the logic to end the user session and redirect to the login page.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPassword Security\r\n\r\nDefine password complexity requirements.\r\n\r\nProvide error messages for users who do not meet the complexity requirement.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nShow/ Hide Password\r\n\r\nAdd checkbox to toggle password visibility.\r\n\r\nImplement frontend logic to show/ hide the password.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nReset Password for Returning User\r\n\r\nImplement email-based OTP receiving method.\r\n\r\nUse OTP to get reset password functionality.\r\n\r\nRedirect to login page to reenter the new password created.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nReset Password for Logged-In User\r\n\r\nEnable user to enter the existing password.\r\n\r\nFunctionality to enter and reenter the password.\r\n\r\nProvide error and success message for user for error or successful execution.  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nUpdate Profile Information\r\n\r\nEnable users to edit their profile information.\r\n\r\nProvide error and success message for user for error or successful execution.  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDocument Management System (DM) \r\n\r\nS.N.\r\n