	(56, 2, 'Guidelines for Week 5 Assignment.docx', 13808, 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document', 'Guidelines for Week 5 Assignment: Tax Comparison Essay\r\n\r\nThe tax comparison essay has the following requirements:\r\n\r\n You can base your essay to compare different taxes and their impact considering:\r\n\r\nOECD countries\r\n\r\nAny 10 Asian countries\r\n\r\nAny other 10 countries across continents\r\n\r\nFirst you need to find the most recent data on the different tax rates as are relevant to the subject matter of the essay.\r\n\r\nFind relevant literature (textbooks and peer reviewed journal articles) that show the relationship between the variables related to the question:\r\n\r\nDifferent types of taxes and business location decision\r\n\r\nImpact of income tax on earnings; decision to migrate based on income tax differences between countries\r\n\r\nTaxes affecting retirement income and savings; Taxes relevant to choice of retirement location \r\n\r\nConsider at least income tax (business and individual), property, and sales taxes in your analysis.\r\n\r\nYour reference list should have at least one source of data, one textbook, and one journal article showing the relationship between tax and each variable under consideration (the relationships being business tax and/or property tax and business location decision; income tax and employment location decision; and sales tax and /or property tax and retirement location decision).\r\n\r\nBased on the analysis you need to come up with three conclusions: the most business friendly country from the category you have chosen; the country most favorable for employment; and the country most favorable for retirement.', 'The tax comparison essay has the following requirements. Find relevant literature (textbooks and peer reviewed journal articles) that show the relationship between the variables related to the question. Consider at least income tax (business and individual), property, and sales taxes in your analysis. Based on the analysis you need to come up with three conclusions: the most business friendly country from the category you have chosen.', 1, 'guidelines-for-week-5-assignmentdocx', '2024-02-10 11:28:49', '2024-02-11 19:53:23'),
